Title: Star-Product and Massless Free Field Dynamics in $AdS_4$
Authors: K.I.Bolotin and M.A.Vasiliev (Lebedev Physical Institute)
Comments: LaTex, 12 pages, no figures; minor correction, the version to appear
  in Physics Letters B
Report-no: FIAN/TD/31--99
Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B479 (2000) 421-428
\\
  Generic solution of free equations for massless fields of an arbitrary spin
in $AdS_4$ is built in terms of the star-product algebra with spinor generating
elements. A class of "plane wave" solutions is described explicitly.
